usage: hwdaemon.py [-h] [--log-file LOGFILE] [-v LEVEL] HWCONF

Standalone script used as a launcher for the Homewatcher daemon.

positional arguments:
  HWCONF                use HWCONF as homewatcher configuration.

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --log-file LOGFILE    output daemon's activity to LOGFILE rather than on
                        standard output.
  -v LEVEL, --verbosity LEVEL
                        set verbosity level.
